short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension that integrates Rate my Professor with the UT course schedule

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension enhances the course selection process for students by conveniently integrating Rate My Professors links directly into the University of Texas course schedule for most professors.
